longBusinessSummary: LAVA Medtech Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. It intends to acquire assets and businesses through a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Waltham, Massachusetts. LAVA Medtech Acquisition Corp. is a subsidiary of LAVA Medtech Sponsor LP.
